incrementWeightBy

void incrementWeightBy(double v)
Increment the weight of this node by the given amount. This will cause the weights of the ancestor nodes to be inconsistent, so it will likely be necessary to call propagateWeightFromBelow on theroot.

Parameters:
v - the double
